	&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		Founded by Sri Chinmoy in 1987, the World Harmony Run is a global torch relay that seeks to inspire international friendship and understanding.&amp;nbsp; To learn more about the Run in Canada and around the world visit the website &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.worldharmonyrun.org&quot;&gt;World Harmony Run&lt;/a&gt; or view our &lt;a href=&quot;/files/ca/WHR%20Cdn%20brochure%20web.pdf&quot;&gt;brochure&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
