<item>
 <title>Manhattan Festival of Meditation 2013</title>
 <link>http://www.srichinmoycentre.org/node/13156</link>
 <description>
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nycmeditation.org/meditation-workshop/&quot; title=&quot;Meditation Workshop&quot;&gt;Festival of Meditation and Spirituality - March 2013 in Manhattan &lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	All events are FREE, seating is on a first come first serve basis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;
	&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nycmeditation.org/meditation-workshop/&quot; title=&quot;Meditation Workshop&quot;&gt;Meditation Workshop&lt;/a&gt; &amp;ndash; Day 1&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Friday, March 8th, 7:30 p.m. &amp;ndash; 9:30 p.m.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;
	&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nycmeditation.org/concert/&quot; title=&quot;Concert of Music and Meditation&quot;&gt;Concert of Music and Meditation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
